- Dwemer artifact identification and valuation
- Survival skills in harsh environments
- Basic knowledge of Dwemer machinery and architecture
- Proficient in light combat techniques
{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Ulyn's journal entries reveal a direct, practical tone with minimal embellishment. He uses specialized terminology when discussing Dwemer artifacts and ruins. His writing is terse and focused on observations rather than emotions, with occasional dry humor about the dangers of his profession.{% endblock %}